<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Career Agent - Proactive Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        :root {
            --navy: #1e3a8a;
            --navy-light: #2563eb;
            --navy-dark: #1e2a5e;
            --green: #10b981;
            --green-light: #d1fae5;
            --green-dark: #065f46;
            --bg: #f0f4ff;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text: #1f2937;
            --text-light: #6b7280;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --accent-orange: #f59e0b;
            --accent-red: #ef4444;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark), var(--navy));
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(30,58,138,0.15);
        }
        .header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
        .logo {
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: var(--green);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem; color: white;
        }
        .header h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .header h1 span { color: var(--green); }
        .agent-status {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .status-dot {
            width: 8px; height: 8px;
            background: var(--green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.3); }
        }

        /* Layout */
        .dashboard {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Cards */
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,58,138,0.1); }
        .card-header {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .card-header .icon {
            width: 32px; height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .card-header h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .card-header .badge {
            margin-left: auto;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* User Monitoring Section */
        .user-section { grid-row: 1 / 3; }
        .profile-avatar {
            width: 64px; height: 64px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-light));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        }
        .profile-name { text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .profile-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
        .profile-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .tag {
            padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .tag-blue { background: #dbeafe; color: var(--navy); }
        .tag-green { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green-dark); }
        .tag-orange { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }

        .status-section { margin-top: 1.2rem; }
        .status-item {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.7rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .status-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .status-label { color: var(--text-light); }
        .status-value { font-weight: 600; }
        .status-active { color: var(--green); }

        /* Briefing Section */
        .briefing-section { grid-column: 2; }
        .briefing-inner {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            .briefing-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        .briefing-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5, #d1fae5);
            border: 2px solid var(--green);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .briefing-highlight::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 4px; height: 100%;
            background: var(--green);
        }
        .briefing-time {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--green-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .briefing-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .match-score {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem;
            background: var(--green);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .briefing-details { margin-top: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text); }
        .briefing-details li { margin-bottom: 0.3rem; padding-left: 0.5rem; }

        .briefing-list { list-style: none; }
        .briefing-item-wrap {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .briefing-item-wrap:hover { background: #f9fafb; }
        .briefing-item-wrap .briefing-item { border: none; padding: 0.3rem 0; margin-bottom: 0; }
        .briefing-item {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .briefing-item:hover { background: #f9fafb; }
        a.briefing-item { cursor: pointer; }
        a.briefing-item:hover { background: #eef6ff; border-color: var(--navy-light); }
        a.briefing-highlight:hover { border-color: var(--green-dark); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(16,185,129,0.15); }
        .briefing-item .score {
            min-width: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 0.3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .score-high { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green-dark); }
        .score-mid { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .briefing-item .info { flex: 1; }
        .briefing-item .info h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .briefing-item .info p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); }
        .briefing-item .deadline {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* Gap Analysis & Action Plan */
        .action-section { grid-column: 2; }
        .gap-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
        .gap-card {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .gap-card h4 { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .gap-card ul { list-style: none; font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .gap-card li { padding: 0.3rem 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
        .gap-card li::before { font-size: 0.7rem; }
        .has-skill li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--green); font-weight: bold; }
        .needs-skill li::before { content: '△'; color: var(--accent-orange); font-weight: bold; }

        /* Timeline */
        .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 6px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--green), var(--navy-light));
        }
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 1.2rem;
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }
        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -1.5rem; top: 4px;
            width: 12px; height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--green);
            border: 2px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--green);
        }
        .timeline-item.future::before { background: var(--navy-light); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--navy-light); }
        .timeline-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); font-weight: 600; }
        .timeline-content { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; }
        .timeline-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); }

        /* Progress bar */
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--navy-light));
            transition: width 1s ease;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .dashboard {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .user-section { grid-row: auto; }
            .gap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* View Toggle Buttons */
        .view-toggle {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .view-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--navy-light); color: var(--navy); }
        .view-toggle.active {
            border-color: var(--navy);
            background: var(--navy);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Calendar Grid */
        .calendar-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
            gap: 2px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .cal-day-name {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 0.4rem 0;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }
        .cal-cell {
            min-height: 70px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.3rem;
            background: white;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .cal-cell.empty { border: none; background: transparent; }
        .cal-cell.today { background: #eff6ff; border-color: var(--navy-light); }
        .cal-date { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
        .cal-event {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            padding: 0.15rem 0.3rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
        .cal-event.agent { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green-dark); }
        .cal-event.personal { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }

        /* Calendar period bar */
        .cal-period-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-light));
            border-radius: 2px;
            margin: 0.2rem 0;
        }
        .cal-period-bar.start { border-radius: 2px 0 0 2px; margin-right: -3px; }
        .cal-period-bar.middle { border-radius: 0; margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; }
        .cal-period-bar.end { border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0; margin-left: -3px; }
        .cal-period-bar.single { border-radius: 2px; }
        .cal-period-label {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
        .cal-task-text {
            font-size: 0.63rem;
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-top: 0.15rem;
        }
        .cal-personal-text {
            font-size: 0.63rem;
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 0.1rem;
        }

        /* Settings Modal */
        .modal-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            z-index: 1000;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .modal-overlay.show { display: flex; }
        .modal {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 500px;
            max-height: 85vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .modal h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--navy); }
        .modal-field { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .modal-field label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .modal-field input, .modal-field select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .modal-field input:focus, .modal-field select:focus { border-color: var(--navy-light); }
        .modal-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        .modal-actions button {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .modal-actions button:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
        .btn-save { background: var(--navy); color: white; }
        .btn-cancel { background: var(--border); color: var(--text); }

        /* Settings button */
        .settings-btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            padding: 0.7rem;
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .settings-btn:hover { border-color: var(--navy-light); color: var(--navy); background: #eff6ff; }

        /* Feedback buttons */
        .feedback-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            padding-top: 0.5rem;
            border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
        }
        .feedback-btn {
            padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .feedback-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .feedback-btn.like { color: var(--green-dark); border-color: var(--green); }
        .feedback-btn.like:hover { background: var(--green-light); }
        .feedback-btn.like.active { background: var(--green); color: white; border-color: var(--green); }
        .feedback-btn.dislike { color: #dc2626; border-color: #fca5a5; }
        .feedback-btn.dislike:hover { background: #fef2f2; }
        .feedback-btn.dislike.active { background: #dc2626; color: white; border-color: #dc2626; }
        .feedback-btn.active { pointer-events: none; }
        .feedback-toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
            background: var(--navy);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            z-index: 2000;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .feedback-toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }

        /* Feedback Panel */
        .feedback-panel {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem;
            height: fit-content;
        }
        .feedback-panel h3 {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .fb-program {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .fb-program:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
        .fb-program-name {
            flex: 1;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .fb-btns { display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .fb-btn {
            width: 28px; height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .fb-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.15); }
        .fb-btn.like-active { background: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); }
        .fb-btn.dislike-active { background: #ef4444; border-color: #ef4444; }
        .fb-textarea {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 60px;
            outline: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .fb-textarea:focus { border-color: var(--navy-light); }
        .fb-submit {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            background: var(--navy);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .fb-submit:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
            <div class="logo">SC</div>
            <h1>SSG <span>Campus</span></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-status">
            <div class="status-dot"></div>
            <span>에이전트 활성 · 마지막 스캔: 오늘 04:32 AM</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Dashboard Grid -->
    <main class="dashboard">

        <!-- [1] User Monitoring Section -->
        <section class="card user-section">
            <div class="card-header">
                <div class="icon" style="background:#dbeafe;color:var(--navy);">👤</div>
                <h2>프로필</h2>
                <span class="badge" style="background:var(--green-light);color:var(--green-dark);">LIVE</span>
            </div>

            <div class="profile-avatar">부</div>
            <div class="profile-name">부솔민</div>
            <div class="profile-sub">글로벌협업전공 · 1학년</div>

            <div class="profile-tags">
                <span class="tag tag-blue">국제개발협력</span>
                <span class="tag tag-green">ODA</span>
                <span class="tag tag-orange">글로벌 거버넌스</span>
                <span class="tag tag-blue">SDGs</span>
            </div>

            <div class="status-section">
                <h3 style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:var(--navy);">📊 현재 상태 트래킹</h3>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">학교</span>
                    <span class="status-value">숙명여자대학교</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">학과</span>
                    <span class="status-value">글로벌협업전공</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">학업 상태</span>
                    <span class="status-value status-active">● 시험 종료 (활동 최적기)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">성적</span>
                    <span class="status-value">GPA 3.8 / 4.5</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">관심사</span>
                    <span class="status-value">ODA · 국제개발 · SDGs</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">활동 가용 시간</span>
                    <span class="status-value">주 30시간+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">선호 활동 유형</span>
                    <span class="status-value">대외활동 · 공모전</span>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item">
                    <span class="status-label">어학 역량</span>
                    <span class="status-value">영어 (중상) · 불어 (초급)</span>
                </div>
